WFKAL MODEL
///---\\\
:GRAPH COMPARE
:TITLE Actual Inventory versus potential measurement
:SCALE
:VAR inventory|Actual Inventory (data.vdf)
:DATASET data
:VAR meas inventory|Measured Inventory (data.vdf)
:DATASET data
:VAR inventory|Simple Simulation (simple.vdf)
:DATASET simple
:VAR inventory|Kalman Filtering (filter.vdf)
:DATASET filter

:GRAPH COMPARE2
:TITLE Actual Inventory versus estimate based on workforce measurement
:SCALE
:VAR inventory|Actual Inventory (data.vdf)
:DATASET data
:SCALE
:VAR inventory|Simple simulation (simple.vdf)
:DATASET simple
:SCALE
:VAR inventory|Filter Estimate (filter2.vdf)
:DATASET filter2
